<h2>How it works</h2>
<p>
  Pure editor code with zero dependencies. On first use it downloads the CLI
  binary from GitHub Releases; the window shells out to it for every diff.
  Requires Unity 2022.3 or newer.
</p>

<h2>Install</h2>
<pre><code>openupm add com.hashiiiii.prefablens</code></pre>
<p>Or the Package Manager git URL: <code>https://github.com/hashiiiii/PrefabLens.git?path=editor</code></p>
